data.description: Welcome home to this 4 bedroom / 3 full bath home!  Upon entering the home you will be wowed with the wooden staircase that leads to 2 bedrooms, full bath and a bonus space that can be utilized as a media room, game room, sitting area or build a wall and have a 5th bedroom! Living room is accented with a corner fireplace and wood floors that is open to the dining and kitchen areas.  Kitchen is great in design with a large snack bar, walk in pantry and beautiful copper farmhouse sink.  Just off of the kitchen is a bedroom and full bath.  Primary suite is nice in design with H/H vanities and walk in closets, separate water closet, standup shower and soaking tub.  There is an abundance of storage in all bedrooms along with a huge walk in closet that is nicely tucked under the stairwell.  The rear of the home is flanked with a wall of windows which allows natural light and fantastic views of the covered patio as well as the large fenced back yard.  There is ample concrete parking with a double gate leading to the back yard for easy access. Call for your private showing today!
